Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.39,0:00:04.65,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:07.35,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged a vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:12.52,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:17.66,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:30.41,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The future that the forbidden fruit foretells...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.62,0:00:38.86,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change the dream into reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:50.73,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The ending that everybody wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:54.00,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.08,0:00:56.77,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged our vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.85,0:01:01.65,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:07.12,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someday I'll show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:16.43,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A bright and ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:54.05,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}Shinigami Realm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:05.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?\NTwo death's heads again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:09.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! I win.\NDon't hold it against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:13.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Ryuk...wanna join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:15.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Join us for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:20.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:30.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do a thing,\Nbut he still got upset...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:32.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:34.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Yagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:37.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please translate the sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:43.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow the teachings of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:47.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the blessings of the sea\Nwill become bountiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:50.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And there will be no storms.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:55.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, at approximately 11 a.m. in\NKanagawa Prefecture in Yokohama,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the body of a man appearing\Nto be about 30 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,was found in an apartment,\Ncovered in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:03.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanagawa Police have opened\Na homicide investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:04.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other news...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:06.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, shortly after noon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:10.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoki Kofuji, 35, was arrested\Nin connection with the murder of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:14.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a 25-year-old female\Nhe was living with
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:18.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in the Shibuya district\Nof Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:24.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Day in and day out...\Nthe same thing over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:29.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... so ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This world...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...is rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:44.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You went to see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:48.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was such a waste of time.\NI shoulda asked for a refund!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:49.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you did watch it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:28.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Death Note...\Ndirectly translated, a notebook of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:33.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How to use it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:37.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The human whose name is written\Nin this note...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:38.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,shall die?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:42.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:46.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:50.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no different than a chain letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:53.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"The human whose name is written\Nin this note shall die..."? C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:07.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...\Nsomething's the matter with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:13.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This note will not take effect unless the\Nwriter has the person's face in their mind
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when writing his/her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:15.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:19.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People sharing the same name\Nwill not be affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:22.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the cause of death is written
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,within 40 human seconds\Nof writing the person's name,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:25.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:29.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the cause of death is not specified,\Nthe person will simply die of a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:31.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After writing the cause of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:36.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,details of the death should be written\Nin the next 6 minutes and 40 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:41.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph... So you can let people die\Npeacefully or make them suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:45.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A prank this intricate\Nisn't too bad, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Write in their name and they die, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:58.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:15.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone actually dies,\Ndoes that make me a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:24.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The assailant who killed\Nsix people yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:29.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,at a busy shopping district\Nin Shinjuku...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:31.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,has now taken eight people hostage,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:34.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,including children and teachers,\Nin this daycare center.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police have now identified\Nthe suspect as
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:39.08,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(111,213)}Kurou Otoharada (42)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:39.08,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(168,110)}Unemployed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:39.08,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(316,378)}Shinjuku Random Killing Incident
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:39.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,42-year-old Kurou Otoharada,\Nunemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:41.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police will begin negotiations\Nwith the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.63,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz19.319\pos(292,295)}Kurou Otoharada
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:51.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A heart attack in\Nforty seconds...right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that is not clear at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:59.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't help but be worried\Nfor the hostages right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:00.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:02.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This has been a report from the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:04.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:06.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Mr. Hashimoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:10.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm hoping for\Na quick resolution to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There seems to be\Nsomething happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The hostages are coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:24.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They all seem to be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And now it looks like\Nthe SWAT team is entering!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:28.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the suspect been arrested?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:31.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:35.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We just received word that the suspect\Nhas died inside the daycare center!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:37.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The suspect is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:38.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:41.02,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{pos(169,243)\frx10\fry354\frz322.949\pos(187,258)}Kurou Otoharada
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:44.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police are strongly denying\Nthat they shot the suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:48.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then could he have felt cornered...\Nand committed suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:52.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,According to one of the hostages,\N"the suspect just suddenly collapsed."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:54.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A heart attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a coincidence.\NIt's gotta be coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:03.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:08.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost 6:30. Don't you have\Nyour prep course tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm getting ready now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:13.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Death Note...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:16.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if this really works...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's worth testing it once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:23.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess it has to be another criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:26.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it can't be someone too famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:30.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he dies, it's possible news\Nof it will be hushed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:32.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I need an immediate result.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:35.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryo baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is it, Sudou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me some money...\N2000 yen will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:41.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What? Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:42.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sudou...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Shall I kill him?\N- What? You refusing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:49.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'd better avoid people around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:53.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Why should I worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:59.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No one would care if one or\Ntwo people like him died.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:02.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can go to\Nthe arcade after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:05.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maki, wanna party with\Nsome guys tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:07.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:08.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:13.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not here to pick me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:17.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... It's sickening.\NEvery single one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:21.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd do society a favor by killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna come and play with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:31.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Taku!\NYou've got a beauty there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:34.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Takuo Shibuimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:35.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shibutaku, for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:39.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon and join me...pretty girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:41.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:42.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:51.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, grab her...\Nget those clothes off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:52.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:55.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:56.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:58.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.99,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz26.985\pos(340,353)}Takuo Shibuimaru    Accidental Death
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:06.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's see...\NWhat'll happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:10.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:11.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Taku! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This... This proves it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note is real!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:24.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Taku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:26.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He just jumped out in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:51.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been five days...since...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:53.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:54.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better get going...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:57.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Going out, Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is barren...\Neverywhere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:05.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I dropped my Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:09.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really messed up big time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:13.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, weren't you carrying around\Na second one behind the old man's back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:15.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You saying you lost both?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:18.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And do you know where you dropped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:20.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Human World.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:20.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:52.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:54.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're early, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:55.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:11:59.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:04.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... the results of the national\Npractice entrance exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:05.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:07.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:10.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness! Number one again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:12.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really did your best, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:13.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:16.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be studying, so don't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:17.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Light...\NDo you want anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:22.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:24.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:30.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I already have what I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:50.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why so shocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:04.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ryuk, the Shinigami,\Nwho dropped that notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I just saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:10.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already aware that\Nthat's no ordinary notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shinigami...huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not shocked, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:30.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact...I've been waiting for you, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:32.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:37.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think\Nthe Shinigami's Notebook was real...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:43.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but after seeing its results,\NI can act with certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:47.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.\NYou really surprise me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:54.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of Death Notes getting down\Nto the Human World a few times before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:58.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the first one to use it\Nto this extent in just five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:00.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people would be\Ntoo scared to try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:03.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm prepared, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:07.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I used the Death Note knowing\Nit belonged to a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:08.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And now the Shinigami's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:10.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So what'll happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to take my soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:18.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Some fantasy you humans\Ncame up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to do\Nanything with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the Death Note lands\Nin the Human World,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:27.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it belongs to the Human World.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:30.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, that belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It belongs to...me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:36.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want it,\Ngive it to some other human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:37.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:40.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,all memory of the Death Note\Nwill be erased from your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:44.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So there isn't a price
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:45.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...for using the Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:48.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if anything,\Nthere is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:52.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,only the fear and pain humans who\Nhave used the Death Note will experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:55.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you die...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:15:00.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the one to write\Nyour name on my Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think for a moment,\Nthat any human...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:07.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who's used the Death Note\Ncan go to Heaven, or Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find out about it after you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:22.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:24.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:25.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:28.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:32.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some apples,\Nthey're from our neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:34.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so dark in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:36.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll ruin your eyesight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:37.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:39.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom can't see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:45.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That notebook...\Noriginally belonged to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:50.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And since you're the one using it,\Nyou're the only one who can see me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and of course, my voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:53.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only you can hear my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\Nthe Death Note is a bond
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:58.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,between Light the human\Nand Ryuk the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:06.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:08.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you choose me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:11.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:17.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...apples in the\NHuman World are awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you call them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:20.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Juicy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:22.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:24.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah, I didn't choose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:27.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just dropped the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:30.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think you were chosen\Nbecause you were smart?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:32.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't flatter yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:36.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It just happened to fall around here...\Nand you just happened to pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wrote the explanation\Nin English,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the most popular language\Nin the Human World.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:44.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you drop it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:47.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it was by mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:50.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,after you went to the trouble and\Nwrote all those instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:52.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd I drop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:54.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,... because I was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:57.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bored?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, Shinigami these days\Nhave so much time on their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're either taking a nap or gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If others see you studiously\Nscribbling names in the Death Note,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:11.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll say, "what are you working\Nso hard for?" and laugh at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:15.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Writing names of other Shinigami\Ndoesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:18.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But since we live\Nin the Shinigami Realm,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:21.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's no fun at all to kill people\Nwho live in the Human World!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:26.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I figured it'd be more fun\Nto come down here myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:31.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you sure wrote a lotta names.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:33.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why'd you write down\Nthe cause of death
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,only for that guy who\Nwas hit by the truck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Without the cause of\Ndeath written down,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:40.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they all die of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:43.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the best thing about\Nthe Death Note, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can write down\Nthe names of the criminals...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and slowly reduce\Nthe number of evil people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:53.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:58.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Any fool can figure it out if someone\Nis just "eliminating the bad guys."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want the world to know...\Nof my existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:05.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That there is someone\Npassing judgment on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:11.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...what's the point\Nin passing judgment?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:13.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was bored...too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:22.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, I didn't believe it at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:26.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that Death Note has\Nthe supernatural power...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:28.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to tempt people to want\Nto try it at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I killed them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:37.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Two men... I killed them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Human lives...\Nshouldn't be taken so lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:45.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have the right to\Njudge people like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:48.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:50.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:54.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is rotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:57.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And that rotten people should die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:01.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone must do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:05.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it means sacrificing\None's conscience and life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:08.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Things can't stay...like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:12.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if someone else had\Npicked up the Death Note...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,would they be able to erase\Nunwanted people from this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:18.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:22.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can... I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:26.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, only I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:29.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With the Death Note!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll change the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At first I kept writing the names\Nof criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,like I was cleaning up the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:18.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that in time, no one would do evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:22.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,While those guilty ones who truly\Ndeserved to be punished for their crimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:24.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,die of heart attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:27.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,people who were immoral\Nor harass others
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:30.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,will slowly be erased through\Nillness or accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:35.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the world would truly\Nmove in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:42.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I would create a new world of\Nearnest, kind humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:46.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'd be the only one left...\Nwith a bad personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:49.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:50.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:55.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm probably the best,\Nmost diligent honor student in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:58.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And l...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:03.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,will become the god of this new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:08.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:10.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,are interesting, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:27.43,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I dreamed a dream that no one could see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:32.81,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I threw away everything that I didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:41.82,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm holding these feelings\Nthat I can't give up in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:48.22,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Even if my feet fall victim\Nto the shackles of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:52.79,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}In between reality and my ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:58.50,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I can't hold back the flooding impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.57,0:22:05.94,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Because I have a strong desire\Nto accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:11.14,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.25,0:22:21.89,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm not weak enough to believe\Nany of these negative perceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:27.70,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm a trickster who doesn't know solitude
