Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.11,0:22:37.87,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz50.398\pos(594,365)\frx358\fry30}Name: Misery
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:40.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire world is watching...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:45.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to see what happens\Nif anyone defies me... L.
